{"desc":"横口鳚主要生活在温暖的印度洋，别看它们是小型鱼类，但是性情非常机敏，当发现有危险时，横口鳚会躲在管虫类遗留下来的空壳中，以躲避敌害。它们会模仿其它鱼游动，趁其它鱼不注意时，偷袭并咬下其身上的皮肤和黏液腺，甚至是鳞片。","copyright":"印度洋的聪明种群 印度洋内的横口鳚 (© Tobias Friedrich/SuperStock)","copyrightonly":"© Tobias Friedrich/SuperStock","date":"20170603","divider":1,"image":{"name":"OHR.BluestripedFangblenny_ZH-CN10868881606","hd":"/images/5CF8ACE46984062DCF2C98713BF750DDD1C89D95DC570986C09E7609AAB631ED.jpg","binghd":"https://www.bing.com/th?id=OHR.BluestripedFangblenny_ZH-CN10868881606_1920x1080.jpg&rf=LaDigue_1920x1080.jpg&pid=hp","bingtmb":"https://www.bing.com/th?id=OHR.BluestripedFangblenny_ZH-CN10868881606_tmb.jpg"}}